flowchart LR
  Source[UI / CLI / MCP / Plugin / COM / AppleScript / D-Bus / Web] --> Intent[OperationIntent]
  Intent --> Plan[PatchPlan]
  Plan --> Policy[SecurityPolicyEngine]
  Policy -->|Allow| Apply[Apply Patch]
  Policy -->|Needs approval| Approval[User or managed approval]
  Approval --> Apply
  Policy -->|Deny| Stop[Abort with reason]
  Apply --> Verify[Verifier]
  Verify --> Receipt[AuditReceipt]
